{
  "id": "69c161a6e2f2d74388383a87",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:ソフトウェアは何もしないと壊れる",
  "created": 1774281166,
  "updated": 1774281291,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c161a6e2f2d74388383a87",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:ソフトウェアは何もしないと壊れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281166,
      "updated": 1774281166
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cd00000000002b0398",
      "text": "副題：放置したコードは、やがて静かに崩れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281166,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0399",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b039a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b039b",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも〜！今日のテーマこれね👇",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b039c",
      "text": "「[ソフトウェアは何もしないと壊れる]」ってやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281230
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b039d",
      "text": "いやいや、放置で壊れるとか、家電かよwって思うんだけど〜",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b039e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b039f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a0",
      "text": "まあ……そう思ってしまうお気持ち、よくわかりますわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a1",
      "text": "形あるものは風化すると申しますけれど、目に見えぬソフトウェアまでもが……というのは、少し不思議な響きがございますね（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a3",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a4",
      "text": "結論から言う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a5",
      "text": "壊れる、というより「環境との不整合で動かなくなる」が正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a7",
      "text": "要因は主に3つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a8",
      "text": " 1. 依存関係の変化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03a9",
      "text": " 2. 外部環境の変化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03aa",
      "text": " 3. セキュリティ要件の更新",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ab",
      "text": "これは経験則ではなく、業界の共通認識。例えば：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ac",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_rot",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ae",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03af",
      "text": "でたでた、りかの必殺・いきなり結論パンチw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b0",
      "text": "でも「環境との不整合」って何？むずくね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b3",
      "text": "簡単に言い換える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b4",
      "text": "「まわりが変わるせいで、昔のままじゃ動かない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b6",
      "text": "例えば、スマホアプリ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b7",
      "text": "OSがアップデートされると、古いアプリが起動しなくなることがある。あれと同じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03b9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ba",
      "text": "あー！それな！！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03bb",
      "text": "昔のゲームアプリ、急に起動しなくなるやつ😭",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03bc",
      "text": "課金したのに消えるの、マジで萎えなんだけどw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03be",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03bf",
      "text": "時代という流れの中で、静かに取り残されてしまうのですね……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c0",
      "text": "まるで、誰も訪れなくなった図書館の本のように。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c1",
      "text": "そこに確かに存在しているのに、もう開かれることがない……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c4",
      "text": "あやの例え、エモすぎん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c5",
      "text": "でもさ、「何もしないと壊れる」っていうより「周りが勝手に変わる」って感じじゃね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c8",
      "text": "その認識は正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03c9",
      "text": "ただし、それだけじゃない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03cb",
      "text": "コード自体も「劣化」する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03cc",
      "text": "人間が読めなくなる、修正できなくなる。これも壊れた状態。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ce",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03cf",
      "text": "え、コードって劣化すんの！？データなのに？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d1",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d2",
      "text": "物理的には劣化しない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d3",
      "text": "しかし、可読性は時間とともに崩壊する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d5",
      "text": "理由は単純。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d6",
      "text": " 書いた人が忘れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d7",
      "text": " チームが変わる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d8",
      "text": " ドキュメントが古くなる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03da",
      "text": "結果、修正不能になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03db",
      "text": "これは「[技術的負債]」と呼ばれる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281291
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03dd",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03de",
      "text": "https://martinfowler.com/bliki/TechnicalDebt.html",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e0",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e1",
      "text": "まあ……なんと儚いのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e2",
      "text": "書いた方の記憶すら、やがては風にさらわれてしまうのですね（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e5",
      "text": "いやでもそれ、人間のせいじゃんw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e6",
      "text": "ちゃんとメモっとけよ案件では？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e8",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03e9",
      "text": "理想論。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ea",
      "text": "現実は、期限・コスト・人員の制約がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ec",
      "text": "その中で「とりあえず動くもの」が優先される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ed",
      "text": "結果、後から苦しむ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ef",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f0",
      "text": "うわ、現場あるあるすぎて草…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f1",
      "text": "未来の自分に丸投げするやつなw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f3",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f4",
      "text": "未来の自分に託す……少しロマンも感じますけれど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f5",
      "text": "実際には、その「未来の誰か」が困ってしまうのですね……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f8",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03f9",
      "text": "だから保守（メンテナンス）が必要になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03fb",
      "text": "要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03fc",
      "text": " ソフトウェアは放置すると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03fd",
      "text": " 　→ 外部環境の変化で動かなくなる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03fe",
      "text": " 　→ 内部の理解が失われる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b03ff",
      "text": " 　→ セキュリティ的に危険になる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0400",
      "text": "つまり、「何もしない＝安全」ではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0401",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0402",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0403",
      "text": "まとめ助かる🙏",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0404",
      "text": "じゃあさ、結局どうすればいいの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0405",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0406",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0407",
      "text": "定期的なメンテナンス。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0408",
      "text": " 依存ライブラリの更新",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0409",
      "text": " テストの維持",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b040a",
      "text": " コードの整理（リファクタリング）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b040b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b040c",
      "text": "これを継続するしかない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b040d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b040e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b040f",
      "text": "まるで庭のお手入れのようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0410",
      "text": "放っておけば雑草が生い茂り、やがて足を踏み入れることも難しくなる……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0411",
      "text": "けれど、少しずつ手をかければ、美しい姿を保てる（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0412",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0413",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0414",
      "text": "あやの例え、わかりやすすぎて神✨",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0415",
      "text": "つまりソフトウェアって「作って終わり」じゃなくて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0416",
      "text": "「育てるもの」って感じか！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0417",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0418",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0419",
      "text": "正解。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b041a",
      "text": "ソフトウェアはプロダクトではなく、プロセス。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b041b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b041c",
      "text": "静止しているようで、常に変化の中にある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b041d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b041e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b041f",
      "text": "見えぬものにも、時間は等しく流れているのですね……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0420",
      "text": "だからこそ、丁寧に向き合い続けることが大切なのでしょう（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0421",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0422",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161e800000000002b0435",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281192,
      "updated": 1774281192
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0423",
      "text": "よし、今日の結論いくよ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0424",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0425",
      "text": "👉 ソフトウェアは放置すると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0426",
      "text": "「周りの変化」と「人間の忘却」で詰む！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0427",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0428",
      "text": "だからちゃんと面倒見ろってことねw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0429",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b042a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b042b",
      "text": "補足。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b042c",
      "text": "それを怠ると、いずれ「完全に触れない遺物」になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b042d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b042e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b042f",
      "text": "……それは少し、寂しい結末ですわね（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0430",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0431",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0432",
      "text": "エモ締めきたw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0433",
      "text": "じゃ、今日はここまで〜！おつ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161cf00000000002b0434",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281168,
      "updated": 1774281168
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161eb00000000002b0436",
      "text": "#2026-03-24",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281196,
      "updated": 1774281206
    },
    {
      "id": "69c161ed00000000002b0437",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774281197,
      "updated": 1774281197
    }
  ]
}